    • Field Detail

      • creation

        public final java.util.Date creation
        The cookie creation date. This is automatically populated by the system on cookie creation.(cookie创建日期。这是由系统在创建cookie时自动填充的。)

      • domain

        public final java.lang.String domain
        If domain is empty a host cookie will be created instead of a domain cookie. Domain cookies are stored with a leading "." and are visible to sub-domains whereas host cookies are not.(如果域为空，将创建一个主机cookie，而不是域cookie。域cookie以前导“.”存储，子域可见，而主机cookie则不可见。)

      • expires

        public final java.util.Date expires

      • hasExpires

        public final boolean hasExpires
        The cookie expiration date is only valid if |has_expires| is true.(只有当|has_expires|为true时，cookie过期日期才有效。)

      • httponly

        public final boolean httponly
        If httponly is true the cookie will only be sent for HTTP requests.(如果httponly为true，则cookie将仅针对HTTP请求发送。)

      • lastAccess

        public final java.util.Date lastAccess
        The cookie last access date. This is automatically populated by the system on access.(cookie上次访问日期。这是由系统在访问时自动填充的。)

      • name

        public final java.lang.String name
        The cookie name.(cookie名称。)

      • path

        public final java.lang.String path
        If path is non-empty only URLs at or below the path will get the cookie value.(如果路径不是空的，则只有位于或低于该路径的URL才会获得cookie值。)

      • secure

        public final boolean secure
        If secure is true the cookie will only be sent for HTTPS requests.(如果secure为true，则cookie将仅针对HTTPS请求发送。)

      • value

        public final java.lang.String value
        The cookie value.(cookie值。)
